      "text": "Built a React LeetCode-style app in [src/App.jsx](/home/navid/java/app-builder/agent-backend/workspaces/lets-build-a-leetcode-clone-127c/src/App.jsx:1) with JWT register/login/logout, `GET /auth/me` role loading, public problem browsing via `GET /leetcode/problems` and `GET /leetcode/problems/{id}`, JavaScript submission via `POST /leetcode/problems/{id}/submit` plus polling on `GET /leetcode/submissions/{id}`, and admin-only problem create/edit on the `/leetcode/admin/problems` endpoints. It also keeps unsupported product areas honest with visible disabled placeholders instead of fake flows, and the visual system was extended in [src/styles.css](/home/navid/java/app-builder/agent-backend/workspaces/lets-build-a-leetcode-clone-127c/src/styles.css:1).\n\n`python3 verify-frontend-contracts.py .` passed."
